{"tid":1631691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再重申] 緊急法先係政府春袋","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:11:50.000Z","uid":218313,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f418da8dc4080d7aadd9cedb8c51feffbba74f0a","tid":1631691,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔好再俾五毛SPIN 左去和理非VS 勇武</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家白痴政府<span style=\"color: red;\">不惜啟用緊急法</span>去訂立AT-MASK LAW<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前我地話, 緊急法等於開左攬炒開關, 但依家我地乜都唔做??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">公眾其實已經係非常不安</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你見呢幾日ATM 無晒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金管局兩日出左幾次聲明就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要做既係利用呢種<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不安</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聚焦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放大</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再射返俾政府</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">因為根本成件事都係政府攪出黎!!</span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地要做既係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大量既文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如: <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">中共無錢, 緊急法充公巿民財產</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">緊急法立左, 外資急速流出, 港紙汲汲可危</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">緊急法授權警察唔駛搜查令就可入屋</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">緊急法可以凍結巿民資產, 防止走資</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢D 信心危機, 比爆二百間舖, 對經濟損害更大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講無謂野, 得返聽日去儲氣<br />\n再過幾日就無用, 一開工就知功效<br />\n全個連登ASSEMBLE! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: red;\">IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US!</span></em></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb6cfa2b8e6e4a291b1fdbb236085522b46227e","tid":1631691,"uid":297686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:06:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6c5b329801deaf0950ca0ea7fad865a94576e9d","tid":1631691,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets